description	"Bao-Dur

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Carbine (2)
- Ion Rifle (1)
-- Causes Pulse Effect Stun
- Power Fist
-- Causes Knockback

^6Inventory: 
- Medpac (25HP)
- Bao-Dur's Remote

^3Abilities:
- Armor Repair [Hold Use on Allies]
- Ammunition Supplies [Press Use to Drop Ammo]

Bao-Dur was a Zabrak engineer from Iridonia. He served under the Exile during the Mandalorian Wars, and again toward the end of the Dark Wars."